Program: Outlook
Title: 26/01/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00n0f2z
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 30 Jan 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the Indonesian girl who's been reunited with her family - seven years after being swept away by the tsunami. Also Frank Buckley, the Irish artist who's built a house out of used euros. And Ahmed Mansaray from Freetown, who wants Sierra Leone's film industry to rival Nollywood. Show less